# Goal Description

The objective is to overhaul the Etmam application flow to match the new business requirements based on the "InfraTech Tender Evaluation process". The previous complex flow involving Spec Cards, Product Nominations, and granular Cost Estimation tabs is being **completely removed**.

Instead, the application will use a streamlined, fully automated 4-step pipeline that culminates in pushing a CRM Opportunity directly to Odoo.

